code: /**  * Process a request using the given {@code CorsConfiguration}.  * @param configuration the CORS configuration to use. possibly {@code null}  * in which case pre-flight requests are rejected, but all others allowed.  * @param exchange the current exchange  * @return {@code false} if the request was rejected, {@code true} otherwise  */ boolean process(@Nullable CorsConfiguration configuration, ServerWebExchange exchange).
